data.description: This charming Taylor Wheeler home is a 1940's gem! Located right in the heart of the historical Terrace Gardens and surrounded by tree lined streets. You will love the spacious living room with beautiful wood floors, formal dining room and private family room. The kitchen has been modernized while keeping the vintage look. Both living areas have wood burning fireplaces creating the perfect ambiance to relax and unwind for the day. Bedrooms that whisper comfort underfoot with the same wood floors. No detail has been overlooked, even the laundry room finds a prime spot near the kitchen.The backyard is a beautiful canvas ready for your personal touch!
